data.details: I think I shall never see a poem as lovely as a tree! - Joyce Kilmer We also love mushrooms, bugs, edible plants and critters that live in the forest and all things in nature. Make leaf rubbings and leaf mounts to identify the trees of our environment. Take a tree hike around the camp to learn the many different and interesting things in nature!
